channel.title: Errors only with PimpScape
channel.description:
I've been able to run TestScape, I have EVERYTHING, I've been able to edit code for TestScape, all of it. I'm trying to use PimpScape now, as TS isn't working out too good. I get 2 errors when compiling and running the server.
RunServer Error - [img]http://img165.imageshack.us/img165/3032/icchuesvn9.jpg[/img]
Compiling Error - [img]http://img250.imageshack.us/img250/1378/compilererrorrn1.png[/img]
I've installed Java, re-installed it, checked the environmental elements variable things.. It all works, it works fine with TestScape, just not with PimpScape. Any help?
